\n樓價唔單止係土地問題，交通都係好重要因素</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n澳洲個情況 明顯係因為政策失當<br />\n令到住房變成投資工具<br />\n加上供應失衡<br />\n連帶令到房屋市場房價上漲"},{"pid":"5bbf6cdc954c2cdf0006b87a35578b1d594acde6","tid":436824,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>澳洲已經係地多人少<br />\n咁都話有住屋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價唔單止係土地問題，交通都係好重要因素</blockquote><br />\nSydney Trains下個月準備再加密，大部份路線全日起碼15分鐘一班車，上下繁時大約5-8分一班車，而且仲有limited stop services<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知鄉村地區 有無鐵路直去悉尼<br />\n同埋文中所提到昆士蘭州 去悉尼要幾耐??"},{"pid":"54e49baf5165ff167dab9cf905658527af13fee1","tid":436824,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>澳洲已經係地多人少<br />\n咁都話有住屋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價唔單止係土地問題，交通都係好重要因素</blockquote><br />\nSydney Trains下個月準備再加密，大部份路線全日起碼15分鐘一班車，上下繁時大約5-8分一班車，而且仲有limited stop services<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知鄉村地區 有無鐵路直去悉尼<br />\n同埋文中所提到昆士蘭州 去悉尼要幾耐??</blockquote><br />\nQueensland去Sydney就坐飛機啦，另一個州份黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSydney Trai